zing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网预售即将开启</strong></span></section></section></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.8; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在传统时代，你需要什么样的板材，我们就提供什么样的板材。其中会有很多制约因素，比如数量，价格，品质，非标等，客户很难找到合适的板材，厂家也无法充分满足，提供。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> &nbsp; <span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而在互联网时代，你需要什么样的板材，我们就找到什么样的板材。无论你的要求是多么的苛刻，数量是多么少量，品质要多么稳定。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.8; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网具有30年厂家的生产销售经验，整合了家居建材全产业链的上下游资源。在牛材网的平台上预售这一个环节将逐一满足“挑剔”客户的多元化需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 牛材网预售即将开启，敬请关注，让我们一起合作，共赢。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/2d9d9aff-517c-4938-b516-fbb2d77e302b.jpg', '2016-06-03 09:27:52', '', '2016-06-03 09:27:52', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('60', '1', '牛材新闻：杭州家具商会来访', '近日牛材网总部相当热闹，接见了杭州家具商会的商会秘书长马掌法、副秘书长李建锋及商会工作人员一行三人。牛材网总裁邵奇亲自接见。大家就如何合作，促进家具企业的发展进行了愉快地洽谈。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">近日牛材网总部相当热闹，接见了杭州家具商会的商会秘书长马掌法、副秘书长李建锋及商会工作人员一行三人。牛材网总裁邵奇亲自接见。大家就如何合作，促进家具企业的发展进行了愉快地洽谈。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;杭州家具商会是以杭州市大中小型办公家具企业，兼有民用家具、五金配件、板材制造、木工机械、家具原辅料等生产企业及大专院校组成的专业性行业组织。中国社会组织评估等级—AAAA；中国办公家具产业基地称号。商会的会员近200家，企业遍及杭州及周边地区市县，会员企业能提供办公家具、民用家具、宾馆套房、医用家具、图书馆家具、校具、影剧院等。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 马秘书长表示欢迎牛材网作为原辅材料供应商加入商会，可以让家具制造商在成本上获得更大的优势。牛材网邵总强调我们的使命是提供优质人造板材，改善全社会室内环境。与商会的合作可以促进让家具制造商及原辅材料供应商都能在“绿色”的环境中健康持续发展。</p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/a52f9e60-271d-4966-8697-cbc0494e8051.png', '2016-06-21 14:49:10', '', '2016-06-21 14:49:10', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('61', '1', '三聚氰胺板造低碳环保家居', '  牛材网的三聚氰胺板拥有检测报告与环保证明，证件齐全，价格透明。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">任何板材，在制造过程中都必不可少地使用胶，因此成形后的板材都会释放游离甲醛，只要控制在一定浓度范围内是对人体无害的，消费者在认清了板材品质的同时，最应关注的是家具所使用板材的甲醛释放量。 根据国家标准，每100克刨花板的甲醛释放量应小于或等于30毫克;E1级中密度板每100克中，甲醛释放量小于或等于9毫克;E2级中密度板中，甲醛释放量在9毫克至40毫克之间。也就是说，甲醛释放量高于上述标准的板式家具，不宜购买。消费者可以要求商家出具家具基材的检测报告，以鉴别此项指标是否符合要求。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　三聚氰胺本身毒性很小，比较稳定，固化后不会游离毒性。制作家具的三聚氰胺板对空气是否有污染取决于三聚氰胺板所使用的中密板或刨花板基材，如果基材甲醛释放量达到环保标准，三聚氰胺是不会加剧材料污染的，“三聚氰胺板材无任何气味，产生气味的是质量较次的中密度板、涂料使用黏合剂或添加剂中含有甲醛等物质散发的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 3em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;牛材网的三聚氰胺板拥有检测报告与环保证明，证件齐全，价格透明。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/cbc05fa1-bd7c-4cac-967d-9aa4a9596c88.jpg', '2016-06-28 15:56:47', '', '2016-06-28 15:56:47', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('62', '1', '牛材网为三聚氰胺板正名', '　三聚氰胺板是一种普通的墙面装饰材料，就是将带有不同颜色或纹理的纸放入三聚氰胺树脂胶粘剂中浸泡，然后干燥到一定程度，将其铺装在刨花板、中密度纤维板或硬质纤维板表面，经热压而成，经常被用在各种家具、橱柜的装饰上。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;行业外人士认识三聚氰胺这个名词，基本来自几年前的“毒奶粉”事件。三聚氰胺奶粉坑害了多少孩子的未来，以至于大家现如今听到三聚氰胺都避之如虎狼。但是三聚氰胺是个中性词，是一种三嗪类含氮杂环有机化合物，被用作化工原料。不可用于食品加工或食品添加物。作为装饰板材却是不可或缺的材料，且价格便宜，色彩丰富。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 三聚氰胺板作为一种重要的墙面装饰材料，经常作为很多家具的装饰面板材料。三聚氰胺在常态下是不会挥发的。只要不去啃它，是不会有伤害的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　三聚氰胺板是一种普通的墙面装饰材料，就是将带有不同颜色或纹理的纸放入三聚氰胺树脂胶粘剂中浸泡，然后干燥到一定程度，将其铺装在刨花板、中密度纤维板或硬质纤维板表面，经热压而成，经常被用在各种家具、橱柜的装饰上。</p><p><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 20.8px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　三聚氰胺板的优点：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　1、硬度大，耐磨，耐热。能抵抗一般的酸、碱、油脂及酒精磨蚀。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2、表面平整、不容易走形，颜色鲜艳，价格实惠。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、易维护清洗，拿抹布轻轻一擦就好了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;　<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> 三聚氰胺板的缺点：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 封边易崩边、胶水痕迹明显、颜色较少，不能有花边只能直封边，封边花样少直接影响了美观。</p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/d28f4ac9-fe6d-40f2-97b5-300a7d4aa1c7.jpg', '2016-07-08 14:13:02', '', '2016-07-08 14:13:02', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('63', '1', '阻燃板的性能特点', '①阻燃胶合板的吸湿性小，吸水厚度膨胀率稳定，防潮性能卓越，不影响饰面、油漆等二次加工；\r\n②产品游离甲醛释放量≤4.0mg／100g，远低于国标E1级9.0mg／100g之规定； ', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">①阻燃胶合板的吸湿性小，吸水厚度膨胀率稳定，防潮性能卓越，不影响饰面、油漆等二次加工；</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">②产品游离甲醛释放量≤4.0mg／100g，远低于国标E1级9.0mg／100g之规定；&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">③阻燃性能优异： GB8624-2006《建筑材料及制品燃烧性能分级》B级 GB／T8625-2005《建筑材料难燃性试验方法》难燃性材料；</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">④具有较高的化学稳定性及优良的耐老化性；&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">⑤MOR、MOE、IB等物理力学性能指标均达到国标之规定优等品A级要求；&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">⑥阻燃胶合板自身安全环保，燃烧剩余物无毒、无污染；&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">⑦不损害阻燃胶合板的饰面性、胶粘性及机加工性能；</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal;\">⑧阻燃胶合板握螺钉力优良，不腐蚀金属链接件。</span></p>', '/Upload/d3074f21-daf6-4fef-bc9a-a4c9fb988681.jpg', '2016-07-15 13:19:06', '', '2016-07-15 13:19:06', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('64', '1', '阻燃板在施工中有哪些优点', ' 在我国经济快速发展的进程中，各大城市都发生翻天覆地变化，在城市改造中建筑是最火热的一个工程，国家在对建筑材料中的阻燃板需求量越来越大、重要性要求越来越高。阻燃板能受广泛应用，与其特点有很大关联。', '<section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;在我国经济快速发展的进程中，各大城市都发生翻天覆地变化，在城市改造中建筑是最火热的一个工程，国家在对建筑材料中的阻燃板需求量越来越大、重要性要求越来越高。阻燃板能受广泛应用，与其特点有很大关联。</section><p><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、 防阻燃性能好，无毒烟性；</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、 性能稳定，通常使用环境和火灾环境均无释放物；</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、 强度高，可满足风压要求；</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、 耐久性好；</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5、 防潮性能好；</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">6、 抗冲击性能优越；</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">7、 施工质量容易控制，降低成本。</section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">8、 外观整洁，容易做二次装饰。</section></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/cc784ddc-eab3-48bd-9397-df5a5a953720.png', '2016-07-22 15:42:48', '', '2016-07-22 15:42:48', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('65', '1', ' 牛材网首次价格改革：出台阶梯式定价，惠及客户', '买的越多价格越优惠', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">导语：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 牛材网从创立之初到现在，秉着公开透明的原则，网上商城发布实价，交易清晰透明。一步步稳扎稳打的发展，优质的售后服务，过硬的产品质量，赢得了越来越多的新老客户的认可。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为了更好的发展，给客户带去实质性的优惠，牛材网从今日起实施阶梯式定价方案。</p><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">什么是阶梯式定价</strong></span></section><p><section style=\"max-width: 100%