INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('66', '1', '牛材网广告牌霸气登陆上海建材市场', '众所周知，金翔木材批发市场是上海最大的木材批发市场之一，而且存在时间之久，可以算得上是老牌木材批发市场。只要从事木材批发的，就没有不知道上海金翔木材批发市场。\r\n大家跟着下面的图片感受下霸气的广告牌，简单的范儿', '<section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"padding: 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-width: 0.1em; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0.1em; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 1.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">8月2日，工人师傅们匆匆忙忙把牛材网的广告牌装上建材市场的大门上</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">8月3日，小编就隔着屏幕指挥现场粗糙的汉纸拍几张美丽的照片</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">8月4日，全国各地支持关注牛材网的小伙伴们就跟着一起欢呼喜悦啦</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广告牌的地点：上海金翔木材批发市场</strong></span></p><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;