INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('73', '1', '牛材网成就板材企业互联网+新时代  “品牌供应商”火热招商中', '牛材网，互联网板材超市\r\n ', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">牛材网，互联网板材超市</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">免费仓储</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">帮助板材企业快速打开销路，销往全国各地</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">牛材网现有四大城市仓储，布局全国，贴近板材终端客户</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">板材团购</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">直接降库存，快速回笼资金，产品直达千万家终端企业</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">牛材网拥有大量终端厂家，一站式满足多元化板材需求。交易便捷，快速回款，从根本上维护板材企业的利益</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">品牌直销</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">板材品牌，深入终端群体</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">牛材网作为互联网板材超市，拥有专业销售团队，宣传渠道，将板材企业的品牌形象深入终端，形成持续品牌影响力</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">牛材网，人造板电商，B2B人造板，防潮材料，密度板品牌，防潮板价格，中纤维板，防火阻燃密度板，阻燃板，FSC密度板</span></p>', '/Upload/da3b45f6-c7a7-4808-849d-cf1165fb1bf8.png', '2016-08-24 15:13:34', '', '2016-08-24 15:13:34', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('74', '1', '巧选家居装修材料 看三聚氰胺板的特性', '牛材网，人造板电商，B2B人造板，防潮材料，密度板品牌，防潮板价格，中纤维板，防火阻燃密度板，阻燃板，FSC密度板', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">三聚氰胺板的特点</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　三聚氰胺板令家具外表坚强，印有色彩或仿木纹的纸本身是脆弱的，在三聚氰胺板透明树脂中浸泡之后形成的胶膜纸要坚硬许多，这种胶膜纸与基材热压成一体后有着很好的性能，用它打制的家具不必上漆，表面自然形成保护膜，耐磨、耐划痕、耐酸碱、耐烫、耐污染。在挑选此种板式家具时，除了色彩及纹理满意，还可以从几个方面辨别外观质量。有无污斑、划痕、压痕、孔隙，颜色光泽是否均匀，有无鼓泡现象、有无局部纸张撕裂或缺损现象。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">三聚氰胺装饰板的性能</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　可以任意仿制各种图案，色泽鲜明，用作各种人造板和木材的贴面，硬度大，耐磨，耐热性好。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　耐化学药品性能好，能抵抗一般的酸、碱、油脂及酒精等溶剂的磨蚀。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　表面平滑光洁，容易维护清洗。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　由于它具备了天然木材所不能兼备的优异性能，故常用于室内建筑及各种家具、橱柜的装饰上。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　三聚氰胺板是一种墙面装饰材料。目前有人用三聚氰胺板假冒复合地板用于地面装饰，这是不合适的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　常用规格：2135mm×915mm、2440mm×915mm、2440mm×1220mm，厚0.6-1.2mm。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　在室内装饰装修中，经常用到，做轻体家具，使用寿命长，加工迅速环保!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">三聚氰胺板基材差别</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　目前市场上面向家庭的三聚氰胺板式家具多以中密度板和刨花板为基材，相比之下，中密度板的性能优于后者。中密度板内部结构均匀，结合力大于刨花板，变形小，表面平整度好，握钉力强。因此，用中密度板做基材的三聚氰胺板更坚固耐用，更能发挥板式家具抵御拼装的特点。刨花板的质地相对疏松，握钉力差，较前者造价低。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\">牛材网，人造板电商，B2B人造板，防潮材料，密度板品牌，防潮板价格，中纤维板，防火阻燃密度板，阻燃板，FSC密度板</span></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/31803a3d-c88a-47ee-bbab-559d83031af6.png', '2016-08-28 14:53:13', '', '2016-08-28 14:53:13', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('75', '1', '倒闭潮席卷而来，板材企业如何应对？', '牛材网认为，倒闭潮席卷而来对于板材行业来说既是挑战也是机遇，板材企业应当正确认识倒闭潮并且积极进行转型升级谋求突破，就能在倒闭潮中成为优胜者！', '<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">近几年随着我国经济发展进入新常态，众多行业面临着洗牌的挑战，倒闭潮向着家具行业、房地产行业等传统行业席卷而来，而与之密切相关的板材行业自然也受到了颇大的影响，那么在如此严峻的形势下，板材企业应当如何应对呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">正确认识倒闭潮</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">倒闭潮并不是一个乐观的词汇，往往带来破产、失业、动荡等失败的现象，对于传统行业来说，倒闭潮席卷而来会让诸多家具行业、房地产行业的中小型企业关门，会让与之相关的板材行业建材行业等失去客源影响发展甚至也会面临倒闭。但凡事皆有两面性，倒闭潮的来临与影响并不全然是恶劣的。</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">　　其一、倒闭潮的来临其实是国家宏观调控的结果，目的就是为了实现市场的优胜劣汰，将一些没有实力、没有质量、没有环保、没有创新的传统企业取缔，同时激励有实力的大型企业朝着高质环保高科技的道路前行；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">其二、国家正在积极进行新常态的发展，让倒闭潮顺势而来，只是为激励传统行业转型升级，不再靠低价竞争获得利润，并没有想要传统行业全部开不下去，所以国家对大体方向还是会有仔细的把控，不会让市场失控甚至崩溃的。</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><br/></span> <span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倒闭潮对于家具企业和房地产企业无疑是很大的打击，对于板材企业来说就更是极大的挑战，不过深究倒闭潮，无非就是一个</span>“<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小企业离场，大企业升级</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的结果，所以板材企业无需过度恐慌，要以稳定的心态和正确的思路去应对倒闭潮的来临。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\">　　</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">首先，</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">板材企业要正确认识倒闭潮，即低质量不环保无创新的小型企业在倒闭潮中是发展不下去的，自以为地位稳固不求转变的中型企业也会面临危机，就算实力强大的大型企业不谋求升级市场份额也会锐减，所以必须对倒闭潮引起重视谋求突破；其次</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">板材企业要积极进行转型升级以谋求突破，从靠低端制造低价竞争的发展模式转变为靠高科技创造技术创新的发展模式，并积极与现代互联网流行趋势对接，跟上时代潮流，在倒闭潮优胜劣汰的过程中升级成为优胜者！</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><br/></span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\">　　</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">牛材网</span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">认为，倒闭潮席卷而来对于板材行业来说既是挑战也是机遇，板材企业应当正确认识倒闭潮并且积极进行转型升级谋求突破，就能在倒闭潮中成为优胜者！</span></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/f2520217-19d3-4bb0-8b9b-c112a65634d5.jpg', '2016-08-30 14:12:27', '', '2016-08-30 14:12:27', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('76', '1', '先定个小目标', '牛材网需要一步一步的努力实现自我价值\r\n那么久先定个小目标\r\n比方说一个月卖他一个亿的板材\r\n那牛材网这一个月怎么做\r\n怎么去实现', '<p>牛材网需要一步一步的努力实现自我价值</p><p>那么久先定个小目标</p><p><strong><span style=\"color:#4bacc6\">比方说一个月卖他一个亿的板材</span></strong></p><p>那牛材网这一个月怎么做</p><p>怎么去实现</p><p><img src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/ab1263e9-80b1-49b5-a748-9cb98fc37f80.jpg\" _src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/ab1263e9-80b1-49b5-a748-9cb98fc37f80.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>牛材网是一家人造板B2B电商，经营防潮材料，密度板，防潮板，中纤维板，阻燃密度板，FSC密度板</p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/14975989-13ad-4a9a-a885-6ae607da49c7.png', '2016-08-30 14:56:43', '', '2016-08-31 13:23:46', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('77', '1', '牛材网智慧云仓（德清站）开放啦', '客户对牛材网的信任与需求，是牛材网提前在德清地区开仓的重要原因。', '<section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网德清仓库开仓了，面积达到4000平米，是牛材网目前最大的仓库之一。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">9月10日德清仓库正式开仓。牛材网上半年的业绩超额完成，目前在江浙沪地区形成巨大反响，对全国的板材市场也有深远的影响。五月份杭州仓库开仓，标志着牛材网在江浙沪站稳了脚跟；而德清仓库的相继开放则标志着牛材网的板材与服务深深地获得终端工厂企业的信任。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">德清地区的工业发展是江浙沪地区的后起之秀，呈现黑马之姿。牛材网的重点客户发展一路从上海，到杭州，再到德清，不止是凭着优质的产品，更是良好的口碑与完善的服务。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">客户对牛材网的信任与需求，是牛材网提前在德清地区开仓的重要原因。</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/edcec166-0713-49f4-82f4-9494dbc8241d.jpg\" _src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/edcec166-0713-49f4-82f4-9494dbc8241d.jpg\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(22, 22, 20); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">免费入驻，云端调控</span></strong></p></section></section></section><p><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网的仓库储备能力居于行业领先地位。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">针对优质厂家和经销商免费开放，助力产品流通，提供云仓储调配服务。</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">德清仓库的开放还有利于减少客户备货库存，对于周边客户的配送更便利，更高效。</span></span></p></section></section></section><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网自2015年12月份正式上线到现在，开放</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上海仓库，合肥仓库，徐州仓库，杭州仓库，德清仓库五大储运中心</span></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，已具备一万立方米现货能力；下一步将在广东，四川，北京等地建立中心仓库，并在华东地区各区域布置县市级设定多级仓库配送点，将仓库进行全国布点，实现全网覆盖，直接提供配送服务，以最快的速度到达客户的身边。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 