INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('84', '1', '牛材网续写不涨价神话', '如今牛材网仓库的存货在一周内拉光了。日前仓库新到了几批板材，继续按照原价售卖。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">自从9月21日起物流运费涨价成为板上钉钉的事件之后，部分物流商运价拟上调30-40%。人造板行业都有不同幅度的涨幅。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上周牛材网保证在现有仓库有货的情况下仍按原价格执行，杜绝跟风涨价。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如今牛材网仓库的存货在一周内拉光了。日前仓库新到了几批板材，继续按照原价售卖。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网以一己之力抵挡住“涨价”压力，将最大的利益留给客户。此次新到的板材数量不多，有需要的新老客户请尽快去仓库看货提货，再次感谢新老客户的支持。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/69273af0-e6a0-4019-aaa9-b16452f6a818.jpg\" _src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/69273af0-e6a0-4019-aaa9-b16452f6a818.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在运费上涨的同时，</em></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">部分商品的跨区域流动也将受到比较大的影响。</em></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">以钢材行业短程运输为例：钢材从邯郸到郑州、安阳地区，从山西到河北等，如果两地价格差距不是很大，那么商品流通将受到运费的制约。</em></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></strong></p><p><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(95, 156, 239); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Emoji Symbols Font&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(22, 22, 20); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网三大仓库地址</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(95, 156, 239); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Emoji Symbols Font&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;, Aria