INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('88', '1', '你不知道为了克服密度板的缺点，牛材网做了这些事', '，牛材网研发的防潮密度板和防霉密度板在基材的生产过程中使用防潮防霉胶，再加入特定比例的防潮粒子，防止木制品因受潮而变形，使家具建材在雨季也能维持坚硬、稳定且美观的状态。由于牛材网防潮板和防霉板表面光滑平整、材质细密、性能稳定、边缘牢固、容易造型，在抗弯曲强度和冲击强度方面均优于刨花板，而且板材表面的装饰性极好，比实木家具外观尤胜一筹。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">木质家具按照材料组成分为实木家具和板式家具两种，其中板式家具是指以人造板为主要基材、以板件为基本结构的拆装组合式家具，因其可塑性强、性价比高等优势受到消费者的喜爱。目前市场有一种声音，很多导购在向消费者介绍板式家具时，会强调他们使用的是目前环保性最好的E0级的密度板材，甚至比很多实木家具环保性还要高，是真的么?密度板到底有什么优势，又有什么缺点呢?</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">密度板的主要优点</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">密度板很容易进行涂饰加工，各种涂料、油漆类可均匀地涂在密度板上，是做油漆效果的首选基材;密度板又是一种美观的装饰板材，表面光滑平整，颜色自然均匀，木皮、胶纸薄膜、饰面板、轻金属薄板、三聚氰胺板等材料均可胶贴在密度板表面上;硬质密度板经冲制、钻孔，还可制成吸声板，应用于建筑的装饰工程中，物理性能极好，材质均匀，不存在脱水问题。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">密度板的主要缺点</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">密度板握钉力较差，由于纤维密集细碎致使密度板握钉力比实木板、刨花板要差很多。此外，密度板的最大的缺点就是不防潮，见水就发胀。在用密度板做踢脚板、门套板、窗台板时应该注意六面都刷漆，这样才不会变形。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网的研发</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为了克服上述缺点，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网研发的防潮密度板和防霉密度板在基材的生产过程中使用防潮防霉胶，再加入特定比例的防潮粒子，防止木制品因受潮而变形，使家具建材在雨季也能维持坚硬、稳定且美观的状态。由于牛材网防潮板和防霉板表面光滑平整、材质细密、性能稳定、边缘牢固、容易造型，在抗弯曲强度和冲击强度方面均优于刨花板，而且板材表面的装饰性极好，比实木家具外观尤胜一筹。</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">牛材网拥有自己研发的实验室，能够研发出各种优良的板材，并以最实惠的价格回报给客户。感谢新老客户的一路支持。</p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/c9c3a6d8-2c27-449e-806a-41d5bf8ed721.png', '2016-10-25 09:12:35', '', '2016-10-25 09:12:35', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('89', '1', '沪通铁路将直通太仓港，木材运费有望降低一半！', '\r\n对于木材人来说运费直接关系到原木、成品的成本，而沪通铁路通车之后，运费成本有望降低一半。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">太仓港地处长江和沿海开放交汇处，拥有</span>38.8<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">公里长江岸线，以及－</span>12.5<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">米深水航道，是江苏仅有、中国难得、世界少见的天然良港。</span></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">自</span>2001<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年</span>11<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">月开展木材进口业务以来，太仓港充分发挥港口区位优势及水路、陆路集疏运网络等优势，不断提高木材作业、检疫和存储、加工能力</span>,<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">木材进口码头泊位由最初的</span>2<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">个增至</span>12<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">个，木材堆场由最初的</span>32<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">万平方米发展到现在的</span>136<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">万平方米，码头木材装卸效率已从起步时的</span>3000<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">立方米</span>/<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">天，发展到目前的</span>20000<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">立方米</span>/<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">天。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">然而如今人民币贬值，韩进破产刺激了国际物流费用的增加，物流超限所导致的成本上升，运输成本全部被分摊到了原木、成品身上，加工厂、经销商不得不面对海运、陆路运费等各方面的因素蚕食了原材料和成品利润的空间。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">沪通铁路是国家铁路“十二五”规划建设的重点项目之一，也是国家沿海铁路大通道和长三角地区快速轨道网的重要组成部分，途经江苏南通、太仓港与上海，线路总长约</span>137<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">公里，项目按国铁</span>I<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">级、设计时速</span>200<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">公里标准建设，总工期</span>5<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年半，建成后，上海至南通火车有望</span>1<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">小时内到达。</span></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对于木材人来说运费直接关系到原木、成品的成本，而沪通铁路通车之后，运费成本有望降低一半。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/bfcfa39a-3ec2-4036-b736-2caa9c005667.png', '2016-10-25 09:30:11', '', '2016-10-25 09:30:11', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('90', '1', '2016年人造板产业发展格局与趋势', '牛材网建议立足行业技术创新，准确定位消费者喜好，并确保木材来源的合法性。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">然而随着当今世界可采森林资源日益减少，而社会经济发展对木材及木制品需求不断增加的情况下，对人造板的需求也随之增加，由此也引发了人造板供求关系失衡、产能过剩、市场低价竞争、产品质量下降等一系列问题。部分企业生产劣质人造板，由其加工制成的木地板、木门等危害消费者健康，造成了市场混乱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　对于人造板行业来说，供不应求的市场和替代性市场是全球性机会。因而，生产出高品质、健康绿色的产品尤为重要。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　全球是一个单一的市场，其产品的竞争力主要体现在交付价格。因此，各国理应在全球范围内控制产品各组成部分的成本。应以最低的成本生产最高质量的产品，提高木材的使用效率，提升产品的附加值，增加人造板的出口机会。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　企业应以消费者的需求为导向，生产出更绿色、健康的产品。因为当消费者需求增长，对木材的质量要求也随之提高。国家间要注重加强紧密合作、交流技术，减少研发成本。2025年中国的制造，智能和绿色是关键，也将会设计出更好的产品，通过工艺技术和设备提高生产效益。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　未来人造板产业发展应该从原材料上把关，积极调整政策、应对挑战，寻求更加绿色的发展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　人造板生产行业：行业洗牌进行时，向上下游产业延伸更易做大份额</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　目前人造板产业仍存在产能过剩、竞争激烈的情况，长期来看环保成本上升将不断挤压中小企业本就微薄的盈利空间，行业集中度提升是必然事件。报告认为未来两种人造板企业具备更强的竞争力，有望在行业洗牌中横向扩张市场份额：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1)本身具备一定品牌效应的人造板企业可选择向下游家居产业延伸，在扩容人造板产品的需求的同时，还能有效增强企业盈利能力<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2)</span>以自有林木资源供给原材料的人造板企业，这类企业的原材料成本波动较小，在下游需求不景气的情况下仍能保证盈利空间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　人造板产业发展趋势</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　目前，人造板市场存在着三大市场趋势，就行业方面来说，尽管普遍的经济大趋势并不明朗，但人造板产业的增长速度依旧可观。就区域来看，亚太地区发展中国家的人造板产业，在2010年<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">-2014</span>年期间出现了<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">62%</span>的增长，这也主要得益于中国消费能力的带动。从驱动力角度，新兴国家的经济发展，需要更多的基础设施原料<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">;</span>随着人造板行业的技术创新，产品质量得到提升，价格也相应增长<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">;</span>同时，消费者喜好的改变，想要寻求更高质量的产品，并对产品款式等有了新的要求，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 169, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以牛材网建议立足行业技术创新，准确定位消费者喜好，并确保木材来源的合法性。</strong></span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/ae62f3e8-125e-4d5a-bba7-d961a2569e97.png', '2016-10-27 16:37:47', '', '2016-10-27 16:37:47', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('91', '1', '板材越贵越好？越重越好？', '牛材网认为，消费者要想选到自己称心如意的产品，必须要根据自身需求出发，不以价格以及重量作为评判依据，纵观多方考量，以避免错过真正的好板材。', '<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">很多朋友在板材选购中仅仅着重于板材的款式以及价格，认为板材越贵的就越好，越重的质量就越过关。其实不然，在板材产品中，未必越贵的越重的对我们来说是最好的。针对自己的不同需求，板材选购也不尽相同。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">板材越贵越好？</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">人们常常觉得贵的板材一定好，其实这只是一种错觉。在板材行业，品牌产品相对较贵，质量也相对较好，但品牌不大的板材产品也是拥有好的质量的，只是名声不响而已。所以说价格高低不是评判板材质量好坏的标准。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">在小编看来，消费者一味选择贵的板材产品未必都好，对一些负担有限的家庭而言，质量优异但品牌较小的板材产品是不错的选择，既节省成本又达到了完美家装的目的，可谓一举两得。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">板材越重越好？</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">很多消费者在挑选板材的时候会陷入这样一种误区，以为板材产品越重越好，其木材含量才会越高。然而，事实并未如此，不同种类的板材产品，其重量是截然不同的。因此，消费者光想使用重量分辨法是不科学的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">一方面，刨花板的重量有时会比实木板材大，虽然制造刨花板的原料使用的是打碎的木材碎料，但在生产的过程中施加了很多胶粘剂，胶粘剂固化后在板材中占相当部分的比例，导致其分量并不轻；另一方面，像柚木、菠萝格等这些稳定性好的木材，它们的密度不高，重量相对较轻，所以说实木的质量好与坏与硬度和重量没有必然的联系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">想要挑选到好的板材产品，不仅要掂量其重量，更要多方考察，看表面做工、木材质量、环保性能等等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">牛材网</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">认为，消费者要想选到自己称心如意的产品，必须要根据自身需求出发，不以价格以及重量作为评判依据，纵观多方考量，以避免错过真正的好板材。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/9fa35128-f7dd-451f-aa49-105d2929ea6f.png', '2016-11-03 09:18:33', '', '2016-11-03 09:18:33', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('92', '1', '市场秩序“拖后腿”，复合木地板发展前景有待考量', '因此，牛材网认为虽说复合木地板优势明显，发展势头良好，却被当下尚不规范的市场秩序拖了后腿，一旦市场秩序规范起来，相信复合木地板发展之路便能畅通无阻。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 33px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">复合木地板的市场秩序尚不规范，主要表现有：其一、地板企业尚在进行不诚实的营销策略，例如过分夸大产品功能，片面强调其中较优异的指标而忽视其他功能，误导消费者，或者是为促进销售，为同一原材的地板起不同的商品名，再附以不同的价格，牟取不正当利益，这种不诚信营销严重侵犯消费者利益，也让复合木地板企业信誉降低；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 33px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">其二、地板企业销售体制不健全，销售上，部分地板销售人员素质不高，对复合木地板性能、作用等相关知识认识不够，服务态度与技巧不够到位，而且企业自身的售后服务体系也不健全，在地板行业普遍存在着重销售轻铺设的现象，导致消费者在铺设装修过程中出现问题无从解决，对地板企业心生怨气，降低了忠诚度和再次购买的欲望。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 33px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">其三、复合木地板市场上“三无”产品层出不穷，假冒伪劣事件频发，例如以国产地板冒充进口地板，在环保、质量皆不达标的产品上贴牌，更甚者还有直接冒充大品牌进行劣质产品的销售，这类事件屡禁不止，复合木地板行规法规又短时间内无法完善，便导致消费者和正规地板品牌权益受损，对后续发展不利。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 33px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">因此，牛材网认为虽说复合木地板优势明显，发展势头良好，却被当下尚不规范的市场秩序拖了后腿，一旦市场秩序规范起来，相信复合木地板发展之路便能畅通无阻。</p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/9baed73e-1222-4979-b7bc-ed12bb4350dc.png', '2016-11-09 14:34:00', '', '2016-11-09 14:34:00', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('93', '2', '牛材网喜获找钢网战略投资 ', '牛材网喜获找钢网战略投资 ', '<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">日前，牛材网获得了找钢网战略投资，双方在经营理念，市场前景，运营模式上均有高度认同。找钢网的战略投资将会大大加速牛材网的发展，同时也将进一步推动了中国产业互联网的发展进程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">牛材网是一家专注于人造板行业的</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">B2B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">垂直电商。从</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">月开始以自营模式运营，整合人造板全产业链资源，以公平的交易环境，完善的服务，诚信的品质，树立了人造板行业的新流通模式。短短半年时间，已经建立了</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">大生产配套基地，服务了近千家</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">终端企业，广受客户赞誉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">找钢网是中国</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">B2B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">钢铁电商的领导者。截止</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">年底找钢网的钢材交易量已超过钢铁行业总交易量的</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">，找钢网和牛材网的战略合作将极大地丰富牛材网在大宗商品电商化的运营经验，助力牛材网成为未来人造板电商领域的领导者</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14pxfont-family:宋体\">。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '/Upload/e87ac7af-3819-4812-9445-df0d2a74b84f.png', '2016-11-10 10:50:24', '', '2016-11-10 10:50:24', '0', '0', '20');
INSERT INTO `info` VALUES ('94', '1', '牛材网两大智慧云仓——黄岩仓和苏州仓正式开放', '庆祝黄岩仓和苏州仓两大仓库同时开业，回馈新老客户,现在来仓库选购板材，有一系列优惠活动。', '<section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 日前，牛材网喜事一件连着一件。继牛材网德清仓开放之后，牛材网黄岩仓和苏州仓在这个月相继开仓，目前仓库数量已经达到七家，遍布全国各地。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;牛材网上半年业绩超额完成，已经在江浙沪地区形成巨大反响，对全国的板材市场也有深远的影响。随着九月份德清仓库的开放，十一月份黄岩仓和苏州仓两大仓库开放，牛材网的仓储网点正在一步步展开。如果说德清仓库的开放标志着牛材网的板材与服务深深地获得终端工厂企业的信任；那么黄岩仓和苏州仓的开放标志着牛材网已经站稳江浙沪的脚跟，并开始布局全国。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 3em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;庆祝黄岩仓和苏州仓两大仓库同时开业，回馈新老客户,现在来仓库选购板材，有一系列优惠活动。</p></section></section></section><p><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">开业活动</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\"></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第一次在黄岩仓和苏州仓购买任意产品满两件以上，赠予</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元现金抵扣券</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">该</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元现金抵扣券，可在第二次购买产品时使用</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">3.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">限于黄岩仓和苏州仓</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">4.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每个客户只能使用一次</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元现金抵扣券，不与其他优惠同时使用 </span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">5.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">活动截止日期：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\">该活动最终解释权归牛材网所有</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/4e90b594-d483-4c53-9334-ba59e9e00a1d.jpg\" _src=\"http://work.99niucai.com/Upload/4e90b594-d483-4c53-9334-ba59e9e00a1d.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14pxfont-family:宋体\"><br/></span><br/></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170); line-height: 2em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">黄岩仓库地址：黄椒路880号（黄椒路靠近四海路）</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">电话：0576-84176030</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">苏州仓库地址：苏州巿相城区渭塘镇凤南路333号（钻石路凤南路叉路口）</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !i